{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/CallToActionWishlist.gif?t=1737993399\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/DiceGambit_Title_Light.png?t=1737993399\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/Steam_Video_Header_Gif_Updated.gif?t=1737993399\" /><strong>Shape and lead your own fully customisable (and debt-ridden) family of Inquisitors in charge of hunting the chromatic monsters infesting the city of Neo-Talis. As your inquisitors cleanse the city, they will unlock unique abilities and grow more powerful, until they retire - or die. Gain favours by hanging out with eccentric nobles, learn the secrets the city holds and occasionally deliver ice cream!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/Steam_Video_Turnbased_Gif_02.gif?t=1737993399\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Navigate the battlefield by rolling dice and use them to control your knights in combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine dice to unleash your characters\u2019 powerful abilities and decimate your foes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reroll specific dice to be the master of your own fate</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapt to the roll of the dice to optimise your turn and achieve victory</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/Steam_Video_customization_Gif_02.gif?t=1737993399\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock over 200 abilities and passives that completely change how your characters play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attend the Academy and pick amongst a plethora of classes each with unique mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shape your characters by freely mixing skills from the different classes however you like</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Break the game by discovering and creating over the top builds and synergies</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/Steamvideo_family_Gif_02.gif?t=1737993399\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Begin your legacy by creating and defining your own Noble Family</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Advance your family agenda by marrying partners with the right combination of skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Incubate new heirs ready for the battlefield with a unique mix of inherited powers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">See your lineage unfold as you lead the chromatic inquisitors from ruin to prominence</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/Stecchi_SteamVideo_Updated_Small_03.gif?t=1737993399\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn favour with the extravagant elite of Neo-Talis and forge bonds to discover their secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your newfound allies' influence to open doors and unlock powerful skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Define your role in Neo-Talis by carefully considering which opportunities to pursue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Who will be your allies as you climb to the top and define your legacy?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812860/extras/Steam_DiscordBanner.png?t=1737993399\" /></p>","background":"https://sha